Type: Package
Package: exvatools
Title: Value Added in Exports with International Input-Output Table
        Tools
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Enrique", "Feas", , "efeas@runbox.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-9431-6051"))
Description: Decomposition of value added in exports in an international 
    input-output table framework, using the methodologies of Borin and Mancini
    (2023) <doi:10.1080/09535314.2022.2153221>, 
    Miroudot and Ye (2021) <doi:10.1080/09535314.2020.1730308>, 
    Wang et al. (2013) <https://econpapers.repec.org/paper/nbrnberwo/19677.htm> 
    and Koopman et al. (2014) <doi:10.1257/aer.104.2.459>. Includes commands 
    for easy data extraction, matrix manipulation, calculation of various
    value added indicators, and other useful tools for geographical and sector
    trade analysis.
License: GPL-3
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports: cli, data.table, methods, openxlsx, reshape2, utils
